1. *Polako* se penjem uz planinu. (I am slowly climbing up the mountain.)
2. *Polako* počinje nova godina. (The new year is slowly beginning.)
3. On je *polako* otvarao poklopac. (He was slowly opening the lid.)
4. Svi smo *polako* krenuli prema vrhu. (We all slowly started towards the top.)
5. Ona je *polako* prešla preko mosta. (She slowly crossed the bridge.)
6. Moje srce je *polako* počelo da lupa. (My heart started to beat slowly.)
7. *Polako* smo koračali kroz park. (We were slowly walking through the park.)
8. On je *polako* slagao kockice. (He was slowly putting together the pieces.)